---
import Container from '../components/container.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<Container>
      <div class="text-xl sm:my-2"> Useful Info </div>
      <p> There is currently no useful info. I will add some soon. I was going to put a cool animal fact here, but I asked Olja what her favourite animal fact was and she said it was that "Octopuses punch fish sometimes". </p>
      <p> Heres a gif: </p>
      <img src="/octopus-punch.gif" alt="Octopus punch animation" />
</Container>
<style>
  p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm) /* 0.875rem = 14px */;
    line-height: var(--tw-leading, var(--text-sm--line-height) /* calc(1.25 / 0.875) ≈ 1.4286 */)
  }
</style>